avdta.vehicle

Class VehTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • avdta.vehicle.VehTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class VehTime
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a tuple of a Vehicle and an arrival time. This is used by the LTMLink class to check when Vehicles have spent at least the free flow travel time on the link.
